cloudberryos (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * M4: parent admin panel (cloudberryos-admin + cloudberryos-admin.service),
    reachable on 127.0.0.1:8766 only, with mandatory token auth, CSRF-
    protected state-changing requests, and constant-time credential
    comparisons. cloudberryos-setup gains the tri-state --admin-panel
    off|local|tailnet flag; the new default (tailnet if Tailscale is
    installed and up, else local) publishes the admin panel to the
    tailnet over HTTPS via `tailscale serve` (never `funnel`).

 -- Sam <s@swh.me>  Sat, 11 Jul 2026 18:00:00 -0600

cloudberryos (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: cloudberryos-setup wizard, curated local homepage,
    squid allowlist proxy, per-child nftables firewall (IPv4 + IPv6),
    GNOME child-account polish, resource-catalog validator, and prototype
    (pre-package) install migration.

 -- Sam <s@swh.me>  Sat, 11 Jul 2026 15:38:41 -0600
